// Hand-owned infrastructure & not-yet-Manifest-modeled tables.
// Reference: schema.prisma.bak. Goal: shrink this file by migrating domain tables
// into manifest/source/*.manifest.
//
// NO datasource / generator blocks here — those live in manifest.prisma (the
// Manifest-generated half of the multi-file schema folder). Models/enums below are
// lifted verbatim from schema.prisma.bak (the handwritten reference), then
// reconciled so the combined folder passes `prisma validate` under relationMode="prisma".




